xbrli:xbrl.in-capmkt:DescribeTheMeasuresTakenByTheE:
Employee well-being programs/initiatives are conducted for all the employees. The following well-being initiatives are being undertaken regularly:
•	Training on Prevention of Sexual Harassment and Code of Business Conduct and Ethics;
•	Standard Operating Procedure for Inspection of Offices;
•	Fire emergency training exit;
•	General health checks up;
•	Access restrictions;
•	Yoga Session.
